"I will lead you to the most fertile plains on earth."
"It is at times like these that one man can be worth 20,000."
"All great events hang by a single thread."
"The clever man takes advantage of everything..."
"Soldiers, your Emperor is in your midst..."
"I will outflank them, and I hope only the debris will escape."
"You are but the vanguard of a great people."
"If he attacks me, I will be delighted."
"If he allows me to attack him, I shall not fail to do so."
"I greatly desire a battle..."
"I have only one passion, only one mistress, and that is France."
"I can give you anything - except time."
